page.title: 10 Occupations
page.content:
This list shows the occupations of all the Heads of Household in the Eastern half of the block:
8 Farmers 1 Veterinary Surgeon 3 Farm Workers 1 Accountant 2 Agricultural 1 Solicitor Contract 1 Land Surveyor Workers 1 Engineer 2 Gamekeepers 1 Transport Manager 2 Groundsmen 1 Workshop 2 Headteachers Technician 1 Teacher 1 Area Sales Manager 1 Food Processor 1 Instuctor of 1 Family Doctor Marine Engineering 1 Army Officer 1 Author of 1 Horse Breeder Children's Books
There are five retired Heads of Household and two unknowns.
